<topic title="Deleting a favorite or tab">

	<section title="Deleting a team favorite or tab">
	
	Mingle and project admins can delete Team favorites by going to the <cref topic="favorites_and_tabs_page">Team favorites and tabs page</cref> and selecting the favorite or tab they wish to delete. 
      </section>  
        <section title="Deleting a personal favorite">
	
	Users and Mingle admins can delete personal favorites from <cref topic="managing_your_user_profile#manage_personal_favorites">users' profiles</cref>.
           
        </section>
